<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">والمَنُّ:</span> طَلٌّ يقع من السماء.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">والمَنُّ:</span> القَطْعُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والمَنُّ:</span> الفَتْرَةُ والإعياء،<span class="c5"> قال الراجز:</span> <span class="c4">[الرجز]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قد يَنْشَطُ الفِتْيانُ بَعْدَ المَنِّ ... وبَعْدَ طُولِ السَّفَرِ المُعَنِّي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلَى:</span> المالِك.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلى:</span> المُعْتِق والمُعْتَق، جميعًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلَى:</span> الوَلِيُّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلَى:</span> ابنُ العَمّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلَى:</span> الجار.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلَى:</span> الحليف.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">والمَوْلَى:</span> الصِّهْر.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والمَهَاة:</span> البِلَّوْرَةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">والمَهَاة:</span> بَقَرَةُ الوَحْش، وجمعها مَهًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والمَهَاةُ:</span> الشَّمْس،<span class="c5"> قال الشاعر:</span> <span class="c4">[الخفيف]</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>ثم يَجْلُو الظَّلامَ ربٌّ رحيمٌ ... بِمَهَاةٍ شُعاعُها مَنْشُورُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">والمُهْلُ:</span> الصَّديد والقَيْح.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">والمُهْلُ:</span> خَبَثُ الجواهر من الفِضَّة والذَّهب وغيرهما.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>